######################################################################
Revision history for Perl module WWW::Google::Drive

0.01 (2016/06/06)
	Started new module WWW::Google::Drive
    	JSON WebToken authentication.
		Methods - new_file, update_file, download, children, children_by_folder_id

0.02 (2016/07/15)
	Used Google drive REST API v3
	Bug fixes

0.03 (2016/11/25)
	added lwp_opts to constructor
	user_agent moved to Moose attribute
	Bug fixes

0.04, 0.05
	Used File::MimeInfo for mimetype identification
	
